  "body": "Using hardhat v2.9.1 still receiving \"JavaScript heap out of memory\" after local fork node being active for few hours.\r\nWhy is memory leaking, something stays in memory forever?\r\n\r\nRelated issue: https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/2380\r\n\r\n```\r\nMined empty block range #14397128 to #14397130\r\neth_feeHistory (24)\r\nMined empty block range #14397131 to #14397133\r\neth_feeHistory (24)\r\neth_blockNumber\r\neth_gasPrice\r\nMined empty block range #14397134 to #14397136\r\neth_blockNumber\r\neth_getBlockByNumber\r\neth_feeHistory (6)\r\neth_getBalance\r\neth_getBlockByNumber\r\n\r\n<--- Last few GCs --->\r\n\r\n[15296:000001CD5B11CC10] 40879168 ms: Mark-sweep (reduce) 2045.1 (2083.3) -> 2044.2 (2083.6) MB, 1409.7 / 0.1 ms  (average mu = 0.183, current mu = 0.124) allocation failure scavenge might not succeed\r\n[15296:000001CD5B11CC10] 40880894 ms: Mark-sweep (reduce) 2045.3 (2083.6) -> 2043.0 (2083.4) MB, 1386.7 / 0.1 ms  (average mu = 0.190, current mu = 0.196) allocation failure scavenge might not succeed\r\n\r\n\r\n<--- JS stacktrace --->\r\n\r\nFATAL ERROR: Ineffective mark-compacts near heap limit Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory\r\n 1: 00007FF6AF277B7F v8::internal::CodeObjectRegistry::~CodeObjectRegistry+114079\r\n 2: 00007FF6AF204546 DSA_meth_get_flags+65542\r\n 3: 00007FF6AF2053FD node::OnFatalError+301\r\n 4: 00007FF6AFB3B29E v8::Isolate::ReportExternalAllocationLimitReached+94\r\n 5: 00007FF6AFB2587D v8::SharedArrayBuffer::Externalize+781\r\n 6: 00007FF6AF9C8C4C v8::internal::Heap::EphemeronKeyWriteBarrierFromCode+1468\r\n 7: 00007FF6AF9D58F9 v8::internal::Heap::PublishPendingAllocations+1129\r\n 8: 00007FF6AF9D28CA v8::internal::Heap::PageFlagsAreConsistent+2842\r\n 9: 00007FF6AF9C5529 v8::internal::Heap::CollectGarbage+2137\r\n10: 00007FF6AF9C36E0 v8::internal::Heap::AllocateExternalBackingStore+2000\r\n11: 00007FF6AF9E8266 v8::internal::Factory::NewFillerObject+214\r\n12: 00007FF6AF71A735 v8::internal::DateCache::Weekday+1797\r\n13: 00007FF6AFBC8F91 v8::internal::SetupIsolateDelegate::SetupHeap+494417\r\n14: 000001CD5CFF2E83\r\n```",
